content: It is not accurate to say that Nordea Bank is a state of the USA. Nordea Bank is a financial services group headquartered in Helsinki, Finland, with operations in the Nordic and Baltic countries, as well as Russia, Poland, and the Baltic countries. It is one of the largest banks in the Nordic and Baltic regions. The Securities and Exchange Commission (SEC) is an independent agency of the US federal government responsible for regulating the securities industry and protecting investors. It is not a corporation.
